Interactive Piper Correction Collection

This project contains a DAgger / interactive correction data-collection workflow
adapted from local robotics code derived from the open-source Evo-RL project:

  https://github.com/MINT-SJTU/Evo-RL

Evo-RL is distributed under the Apache License 2.0. Keep this notice,
LICENSE, and THIRD_PARTY_NOTICES.md with redistributed versions.

The bundled LeRobot-Piper runtime under vendor/lerobot_piper/lerobot retains
its upstream license notices. OpenPI source and policy checkpoints are external
artifacts and are not included in this repository.
